    mtk, after a note by Alex Tuninga
        A fairly significant rewrite to clarify operation of abort().

argz_add.3
    Bert Wesarg / mtk
        s/envz/envz_add/ in SEE ALSO.

envz_add.3
    Bert Wesarg / mtk
        s/argz/argz_add/ in SEE ALSO.
